    "body": "`commands` is not run in a shell and thus does not support pipes. Please try using something like this:\n```toml\ncommands = [\n    [ [\"sh\", \"-c\", \"make -p | rg ROOT | lines | last | split row '$' | last | str replace '(DEV)' '/dev' | fd 'gcc.exe' $in | lines | first | path expand\", \"--version\"] ],\n]\n```",
